<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.11">
<l>nantaṉ matalaiyaik kākutta ṉainaviṉ</l>
<l>ṟunti paṟanta voḷiyiḻai yārkaḷcol</l>
<l>centamiḻt teṉputu vai viṭṭu cittaṉcol</l>
<l>aintiṉō ṭaintumval lārkkalla lillaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who master [these] five and five [verses],</l>
<l rend="Indent">Composed in fine Tamil by Viṭṭucittaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">of Putuvai in the south</l>
<l rend="indent">on the words of the bright ornamented ladies</l>
<l rend="indent">who played a game of jumping and singing,</l>
<l rend="indent">proclaiming [the stories of] Nanda’s son and Kākutstha,</l>
<l>there will be no misfortune.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
